---
import IndexLayout from "../../../layouts/IndexLayout.astro";
import ProductTemplate from "@components/product/product-template.astro";

import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import productImage1 from "@assets/images/products/chaga-extract-500-90/chaga-extract-500-90-fwc.webp";
import productImage2 from "@assets/images/products/chaga-extract-500-90/chaga-extract-500-90-bws.webp";

const alt = "NATIOS Chaga Extract";
const loading = "lazy";
const productImageWidth = 1000;
const pixelDensities = [1, 1.5, 2, 2.5, 3];
const quality = 90;
---

<IndexLayout title="NATIOS Chaga Extract">
	<ProductTemplate>
		<!-- _____________________________________________ -->
		<!-- ____________________NÁZEV____________________ -->
		<!-- _____________________________________________ -->
		<h1 slot="product-name-h1">Chaga Extract, 40% polysaccharides</h1>
		<h2 slot="product-name-h2">500 mg, 90 vegan capsules</h2>

		<!-- ________________________________________________________ -->
		<!-- ____________________FOTKY VELKÉ DO 6____________________ -->
		<!-- ________________________________________________________ -->
		<div slot="large-image-1" class="large-image active">
			<Image
				src={productImage1}
				width={productImageWidth}
				alt={alt}
				quality={quality}
				densities={pixelDensities}
				loading="eager"
			/>
		</div>

		<div slot="large-image-2" class="large-image">
			<Image
				src={productImage2}
				width={productImageWidth}
				alt={alt}
				quality={quality}
				densities={pixelDensities}
				loading={loading}
			/>
		</div>

		<!-- ____________________________________________________________ -->
		<!-- ____________________FOTKY NÁHLEDOVÉ DO 6____________________ -->
		<!-- ____________________________________________________________ -->
		<div slot="preview-image-1" class="preview-image active">
			<Image
				src={productImage1}
				width={productImageWidth}
				alt={alt}
				quality={quality}
				densities={pixelDensities}
				loading="eager"
			/>
		</div>

		<div slot="preview-image-2" class="preview-image">
			<Image
				src={productImage2}
				width={productImageWidth}
				alt={alt}
				quality={quality}
				densities={pixelDensities}
				loading="eager"
			/>
		</div>

		<!-- ___________________________________________________________________________________ -->
		<!-- ____________________SELECT MOŽNOSTI (možnost video a orher 1 2)____________________ -->
		<!-- ___________________________________________________________________________________ -->
		<span slot="select-description" class="select-description">Description</span>
		<span slot="select-ingredients" class="select-ingredients">Ingredients</span>
		<span slot="select-dosage" class="select-dosage">Dosage and warnings</span>

		<!-- ____________________________________________________________________________________ -->
		<!-- ____________________DESCRIPTION DIVY (možnost video a orher 1 2)____________________ -->
		<!-- ____________________________________________________________________________________ -->
		<div slot="description-description" class="description-description active">
			<p>
				The Chaga mushroom, also known by its scientific name Inonotus obliquus, is a remarkable fungus with a rich
				history spanning centuries. Chaga is native to cold climates such as Siberia, Russia, Korea, Northern Europe and
				parts of the United States and Canada. The use of Chaga can be traced back to traditional Siberian and Russian
				folk medicine, where it was often made into teas or decoctions to promote general health and vitality. Siberian
				shamans called it a <b>“Gift from God”</b> and attributed mystical and healing powers.
			</p>
			<p>
				The Chaga supplement provides a very potent extract of the plant. The main active ingredients in the mushroom
				are polysaccharides (particularly beta 1-3-D-glucans). Each vegan capsule contains 5000&nbsp;mg of pure and
				potent extract standardised to 40&nbsp;% polysaccharides, which means the extract is up to 40 times more
				concentrated and potent than the raw powder of ground Reishi. With such potency, you only need to take one
				capsule per day.
			</p>

			<ul>
				<li>Active ingredients obtained through extraction</li>
				<li>Better digestibility and potency</li>
				<li>Standardised levels of polysaccharides</li>
				<li>Traditionally used for centuries</li>
				<li>The effective dose in one capsule</li>
				<li>Contains no additives, indigestible or other potentially harmful substances</li>
				<li>Vegan and GMO-free</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="no-padding"><b>What makes NATIOS Chaga Extract different?</b></p>
			<p>
				When you use a multi-potent extract, you can expect multiple benefits. One is the guarantee of high purity
				because instead of simply grinding the mushroom and putting it in a capsule, the extract goes through
				additional, controlled production steps. In addition, the higher potency allows you to reduce the capsule’s size
				and daily dosage, which you will appreciate when taking it. All this while guaranteeing the same, if not
				greater, potency than products containing raw mushrooms.
			</p>
			<p class="no-padding"><b>What is Chaga?</b></p>
			<p>
				Chaga (Inonotus obliquus) is a mushroom species that grows primarily on the bark of birch trees in cold climates
				such as northern Europe, Siberia, Russia, Korea, north of Canada and Alaska. Chaga forms a woody conk that looks
				like a clump of burnt charcoal with a 25-38&nbsp;cm diameter. Inside is a soft orange-coloured core.
			</p>
		</div>
		<!-- ____________________TABULKA____________________ -->
		<div slot="description-ingredients" class="description-ingredients">
			<table>
				<thead>
					<tr>
						<th
							><div class="dosage">
								<span
									><b>Serving size:</b> 1&nbsp;veg capsule<br />
									<b>Contains:</b> 90&nbsp;servings</span
								>
							</div></th
						>
						<th>Amount Per Serving</th>
						<th>%NRV*</th>
					</tr>
				</thead>

				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td
							><b>Chaga extract</b> (<i>Inonotus obliquus</i>) (Fruiting bodies)
							<br />
							- standardized to 40% polysaccharides
						</td>
						<td>500&nbsp;mg</td>
						<td>**</td>
					</tr>

					<tr>
						<td colspan="3"
							><div class="rhp">
								<span>* Nutritional Reference Value</span>
								<span>** Nutritional Reference Value is not established</span>
							</div></td
						>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
			<p><b>Other ingredients:</b> Veg Capsule (HPMC). The product does not contain any other added substances.</p>
		</div>
		<!-- ____________________DÁVKOVÁNÍ A UPOZORNĚNÍ____________________ -->

		<div slot="description-dosage" class="description-dosage">
			<p>
				<b>Recommended dosage:</b><br />
				Take 1 to 2 capsules daily with water.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b>Warning:</b><br />
				For adults only. If you have a medical condition, are pregnant, nursing or trying to conceive, or are taking medication,
				consult with a physician before taking this product! Keep out of reach of children. Dietary supplement. It is not
				a substitute for a varied diet. Do not exceed the recommended daily dosage.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b>Storage:</b><br />
				Store in a cool, dry place.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b>Made in EU</b>
			</p>
		</div>
	</ProductTemplate>
</IndexLayout>

<style is:global>
	:root {
		--number-of-photos: 2;
	}
</style>
